name: Obakeyashi
description:
Obakeyashi "Haunted House"

You trust your house, right? It's your house. It protects you from the world and, even more important, all the people out there. It sees you naked every day. It knows your sins. It's the only place where you are your true self. So when that gets corrupted, when that becomes haunted, that's terrifying.

Halloween Special

Digital Illustration by ndroy
